No. D-2544. In the Matter of Discipline of Michael H Lubin. 562 U.S. 814, 131 S. Ct. 406,

178 L. Ed. 2d 270,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7527. October 4, 2010.

Michael H Lubin, of N. Miami Beach, Florida, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
